\begin_inset Formula $j\rightarrow i$
\end_inset

 then we say that 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

 
\emph on
communicate
\emph default
, and write 
\begin_inset Formula $i\leftrightarrow j$
\end_inset


\end_layout

